title: Drake, Arnold, Psalm West, MTH and more.
itunes:title: Drake, Arnold, Psalm West, MTH and more.
description:
Good morning it's Monday and let's get after it!  We all find out what each did over the weekend and The CEO talks about his vault.  The Terminator was dropkicked at one of his bodybuilding events in South Africa.  Kim K and Kanye name their baby boy Psalm West.  The billionaire Robert Smith erases the debt of the entire Class of 2019 at Morehouse College.  The GOT Update simply states, "That Damn Dragon got a lot of fire!"  J. Anthony Brown murders another one in the spirit of Johnny Gill.  Drake has the internet buzzin' with his shirtless picture.  The CEO talks about the importance of fighting for your dreams and more in Closing Remarks today.  Have a great weekend!
